data.description: This charming & affordable 2 bedroom home with 2-car garage is nestled in the convenient and desirable Southampton neighborhood.  Situated in an ideal location, the home is near excellent shopping and delicious restaurants. This home is move-in ready and offers updated kitchen, hardwood floors, newer HVAC system and a 2-car garage. The living room seamlessly flows into the dining room, creating an ideal space for hosting gatherings. The well-designed kitchen boasts an efficient layout, complete with a stylish tile backsplash and a solid surface island. From the kitchen, step out onto the adjacent covered deck, which overlooks the backyard and is the perfect spot to relax and unwind. Don't miss the opportunity to make this affordable gem your own!
